TO SHARE A FOLDER ON UBUNTU:

install some Samba stuff
[folder] -> right click -> "Local Network Share"
> smbpasswd -a [username] -> type in the password


TO ACCESS ON WINDOWS 7:

Windows Explorer should find a computer and a network share automatically

cmd:
	> net use Z: \\<computer name?>\<share name>
	> Z: